#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/tips.lua:4 input:4 standard
msgid ""
"There is always demand for experienced workers. Make sure you train your "
"hunters, farmers, coppersmiths, craftsmen, weavers and miners in time."
msgstr ""
"Sempre hi ha demanda de treballadors amb experiència. Assegureu-vos "
"d'entrenar a temps els vostres caçadors, agricultors, courers, artesans, "
"teixidors i miners."

#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/tips.lua:8 input:8 standard
msgid ""
"Basic mines are quicker in training miners because their working cycle is "
"shorter."
msgstr ""
"Les mines bàsiques són més ràpides en la formació dels miners perquè el seu "
"cicle de treball és més curt."

#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/tips.lua:12 input:12
#: standard
msgid ""
"Economy of Sumatrans needs 2 types of trees, palm and tropical trees. Find "
"the right balance between palm planters and jungle preservers."
msgstr ""
"L'economia de Sumatrans necessita 2 tipus d'arbres, palmeres i arbres "
"tropicals. Trobeu l'equilibri adequat entre els jardiners de palmeres i els "
"conservadors de la selva."

#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/tips.lua:16 input:16
#: standard
msgid ""
"Leaf gatherers are important part of your economy, they need cassava fields, "
"plantations and palm planters nearby."
msgstr ""
"Els recol·lectors de fulles són una part important de la vostra economia, "
"necessiten camps de mandioca, plantacions i plantadores de palmeres a prop."

#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/tips.lua:20 input:20
#: standard
msgid ""
"Terraform done by thermal springs is very cheap. It is essential for winter "
"terrain and very useful for dry and mountain terrain."
msgstr ""
"El terraform fet per fonts termals és molt econòmic. És imprescindible per a "
"terrenys hivernals i molt útil per a terrenys secs i de muntanya."

#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/tips.lua:24 input:24
#: standard
msgid ""
"Hunting camps need tropical swamps nearby because warriors hunt crocodiles "
"to improve their attack ability."
msgstr ""
"Els campaments de caça necessiten pantans tropicals a prop perquè els "
"guerrers cacen cocodrils per millorar la seva capacitat d'atac."

#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/tips.lua:28 input:28
#: standard
msgid ""
"Production of eggs may help your kitchens work smoothly. Especially on maps "
"where your hunters do not have fishes to hunt."
msgstr ""
"La producció d'ous pot ajudar a que les vostres cuines funcionin sense "
"problemes. Sobretot als mapes on els vostres caçadors no tenen peixos per "
"caçar."

#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/tips.lua:32 input:32
#: standard
msgid ""
"Study carefully what ingredients do you need to prepare a meal and how can "
"you get them. Meal is essential for training, mining and road traffic."
msgstr ""
"Estudia bé quins ingredients necessites per preparar un àpat i com pots "
"aconseguir-los. El menjar és essencial per a la formació, la mineria i el "
"trànsit rodat."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Log, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:93 input:93
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Log is an important basic building material. It is also used for charcoal "
"production and for the production of sanded wood for tools and spears."
msgstr ""
"El tronc és un material bàsic de construcció important. També s'utilitza per "
"a la producció de carbó vegetal i per a la producció de fusta polida per a "
"eines i llances."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Log, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:95 input:95
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Logs are produced by felling all trees except the tropical ones. Woodcutters "
"need palm planter’s huts nearby to take care of the supply of trees."
msgstr ""
"Els troncs es produeixen talant tots els arbres excepte els tropicals. Els "
"llenyataires necessiten cabanes de plantadors de palmeres a prop per fer-se "
"càrrec del subministrament d'arbres."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Tropical Wood, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:106 input:106
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Tropical wood is an important basic building material. It is also used for "
"charcoal production."
msgstr ""
"La fusta tropical és un material bàsic de construcció important. També "
"s'utilitza per a la producció de carbó vegetal."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Tropical Wood, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:108 input:108
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"It is produced by felling tropical trees (ironwood, rubber and balsa trees "
"as well as dipterocarpus). Woodcutters need jungle preserver’s huts nearby "
"to take care of the supply of tropical trees."
msgstr ""
"Es produeix mitjançant la tala d'arbres tropicals (fusta de ferro, cautxú i "
"balsa, així com dipterocarpus). Els llenyataires necessiten cabanes de "
"preservació de la selva properes per tenir cura del subministrament d'arbres "
"tropicals."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Palm Leaves, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:119 input:119
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Palm leaves are a basic building material. They are used together with reed "
"for cloth production too."
msgstr ""
"Les fulles de palmera són un material bàsic de construcció. També "
"s'utilitzen juntament amb la canya per a la producció de tela."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Palm Leaves, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:121 input:121
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Leaf gatherers need palm planter’s huts nearby to take care of the supply of "
"palm trees. The trees have to be cut down by woodcutters first, then can the "
"gatherers collect the leaves from the ground."
msgstr ""
"Els recol·lectors de fulles necessiten cabanes de palmeres a prop per fer-se "
"càrrec del subministrament de palmeres. Els llenyataires primer han de talar "
"els arbres, i després els recol·lectors poden recollir les fulles del terra."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Reed, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:131 input:131
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Reed is a basic building material. It is used together with palm leaves for "
"cloth production too."
msgstr ""
"La canya és un material bàsic de construcció. També s'utilitza juntament amb "
"fulles de palmera per a la producció de tela."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Reed, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:133 input:133
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"It is planted and collected by the reed cutters on shores of lakes and "
"rivers."
msgstr ""
"És plantat i recollit pels talladors de canyes a les vores dels llacs i rius."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Cloth, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:144 input:144
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Cloth is needed to build several buildings. Also the dressmakers need cloth "
"for clothing for your warriors."
msgstr ""
"Es necessita tela per construir diversos edificis. També les modistes "
"necessiten roba per a la roba dels teus guerrers."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Cloth, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:146 input:146
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid "It is produced out of reed and palm leaves."
msgstr "Es produeix a partir de fulles de canya i palmera."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Granite
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:157 input:157
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Granite is a basic building material. You also need it for production of "
"diamonds and whetstones."
msgstr ""
"El granit és un material bàsic de construcció. També el necessiteu per a la "
"producció de diamants i pedres d'afilar."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Sanded Wood
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:168 input:168
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Sanded wood is used for tool and spear production. You will need it to build "
"a ship too. It is made out of logs."
msgstr ""
"La fusta polida s'utilitza per a la producció d'eines i llança. També el "
"necessitareu per construir un vaixell. Està fet de troncs."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Crocodile Skin
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:177 input:177
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Crocodile skin is used for production of clothing for your warriors, "
"hunters, chiefs and scouts."
msgstr ""
"La pell de cocodril s'utilitza per a la producció de roba per als teus "
"guerrers, caçadors, caps i exploradors."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Water, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:186 input:186
#: standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Water is the essence of life!"
msgstr "L'aigua és essencial per a la vida!"

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Water, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:188 input:188
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Water is used by the cooks in your kitchens. Cassava plantations and chicken "
"farm need water too."
msgstr ""
"L'aigua la fan servir els cuiners a les vostres cuines. Les plantacions de "
"iuca i la granja de pollastres també necessiten aigua."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Cassava Root
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:201 input:201
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Cassava root is cooked in cassava kitchens to prepare starch, the main "
"ingredient of meals."
msgstr ""
"L'arrel de mandioca es cuina a les cuines de mandioca per preparar midó, "
"l'ingredient principal dels àpats."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Cassava Leaves, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:211 input:211
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid "Cassava leaves are needed to prepare sauce for your meals."
msgstr ""
"Les fulles de iuca són necessàries per preparar la salsa dels vostres àpats."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Cassava Leaves, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:213 input:213
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Make sure that you leaf gatherers collect all leaves from the harvested "
"cassava fields. Otherwise you will have to substitute them with eggs."
msgstr ""
"Assegureu-vos que els recol·lectors de fulles recullin totes les fulles dels "
"camps de mandioca collits. En cas contrari, haureu de substituir-los per ous."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Starch, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:223 input:223
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid "Starch is the main ingredient used by meal preparation."
msgstr ""
"El midó és l'ingredient principal utilitzat per a la preparació dels àpats."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Starch, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:225 input:225
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid "It is made out of cassava roots by cooking."
msgstr "Es fa amb arrels de mandioca per cocció."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Fish
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:235 input:235
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Fresh fish is cooked in the kitchens and added into meals for your warriors "
"and miners."
msgstr ""
"El peix fresc es cuina a les cuines i s'afegeix als àpats dels vostres "
"guerrers i miners."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Meat
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:245 input:245
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Fresh meat is cooked in the kitchens and added into meals for yor warriors, "
"miners and carriers."
msgstr ""
"La carn fresca es cuina a les cuines i s'afegeix als àpats dels teus "
"guerrers, miners i portadors."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Eggs, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:256 input:256
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Eggs are used as a substitute for meat, fish and cassava leaves in the "
"kitchens."
msgstr ""
"Els ous s'utilitzen com a substitut de la carn, el peix i les fulles de "
"mandioca a les cuines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Eggs, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:258 input:258
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid "You need food waste as a food source for chickens to produce eggs."
msgstr ""
"Necessites els residus d'aliments com a font d'aliment perquè les gallines "
"produeixin ous."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Meal
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:268 input:268
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Meal is consumed in mines and training sites. Every new carrier also need "
"meal before his service on a road."
msgstr ""
"El menjar es consumeix a les mines i llocs d'entrenament. Cada transportista "
"nou també necessita menjar abans del seu servei a la carretera."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Sumatran ware: Meal
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:270 input:270
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Meal is an optimal combination of several food ingredients. These are "
"starch, cassava leaves, meat or fish and water. Eggs can be used instead "
"some of these ingredients too."
msgstr ""
"El menjar és una combinació òptima de diversos ingredients alimentaris. Es "
"tracta de midó, fulles de mandioca, carn o peix i aigua. També es poden "
"utilitzar ous en lloc d'alguns d'aquests ingredients."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Food Waste
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:278 input:278
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid "You can feed food waste to your chickens and gain eggs and meat."
msgstr ""
"Podeu alimentar els vostres pollastres amb residus d'aliments i obtenir ous "
"i carn."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Sumatran ware: Food Waste
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:280 input:280
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Food waste is produced as a byproduct in your kitchens. Kitchens also start "
"producing food waste by throwing out starch when they don't have cassava "
"leaves or eggs on stock and meal is needed."
msgstr ""
"Els residus alimentaris es produeixen com a subproducte a les vostres "
"cuines. Les cuines també comencen a produir residus d'aliments llençant midó "
"quan no tenen fulles de mandioca o ous en brou i cal menjar."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Palm Wine
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:288 input:288
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Palm wine is consumed together with meal in your training sites and in deep "
"mines. It is produced by winery and wineries need fully grown palms nearby."
msgstr ""
"El vi de palma es consumeix juntament amb l'àpat als vostres llocs "
"d'entrenament i a les mines profundes. És produït per celler i els cellers "
"necessiten palmeres totalment cultivades a prop."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Raw Diamond
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:300 input:300
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Raw diamonds are used to produce whetstones or can be polished and used as a "
"precious building material."
msgstr ""
"Els diamants en brut s'utilitzen per produir pedres d'amolar o es poden "
"polir i utilitzar com a material de construcció preciós."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Diamond, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:310 input:310
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"Diamonds are a very precious building material. These precious stones are "
"also your main source of wealth, when goal of game is to collect precious "
"things."
msgstr ""
"Els diamants són un material de construcció molt preciós. Aquestes pedres "
"precioses també són la vostra principal font de riquesa, quan l'objectiu del "
"joc és recollir coses precioses."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Diamond, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:312 input:312
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid "The production of diamonds is skipped when whetstone is needed."
msgstr "La producció de diamants es salta quan es necessita pedra d'esmolar."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Coal, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:323 input:323
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"While smelting metals, the fires of the sumatran furnaces are fed with coal."
msgstr ""
"Mentre es fonen metalls, els focs dels forns de sumatra s'alimenten amb "
"carbó."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Coal, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:325 input:325
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid ""
"It is mined in coal mines or produced out of logs and tropical wood by a "
"charcoal kiln."
msgstr ""
"S'extreu a les mines de carbó o es produeix amb troncs i fusta tropical "
"mitjançant un forn de carbó vegetal."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran ware: Copper Ore, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:336 input:336
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_ware"
msgid "Copper ore can be smelted into copper in a furnace."
msgstr "El mineral de coure es pot fondre en coure en un forn."

