"Els filons de carbó contenen minerals que es poden extreure amb mines de "
"carbó."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran resource indicator: Coal, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1104 input:1104
#: standard
msgid "There is only a little bit of coal here."
msgstr "Aquí només hi ha una mica de carbó."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran resource indicator: Iron, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1113
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1157 input:1113
#: input:1157 standard
msgid "This vein contains iron ore that can be dug up by iron mines."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta vena conté mineral de ferro que pot ser excavat per mines de ferro."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran resource indicator: Iron, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1115 input:1115
#: standard
msgid "There is only a little bit of iron ore here."
msgstr "Aquí només hi ha una mica de mineral de ferro."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran resource indicator: Copper-Gold, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1124
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1168 input:1124
#: input:1168 standard
msgid ""
"This vein contains copper-gold ore that can be dug up by copper-gold mines."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta vena conté mineral de coure-or que pot ser excavat per mines de "
"coure-or."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran resource indicator: Copper-Gold, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1126 input:1126
#: standard
msgid "There is only a little bit of copper-gold ore here."
msgstr "Aquí només hi ha una mica de mineral de coure i or."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran resource indicator: Stones, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1135
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1179 input:1135
#: input:1179 standard
msgid ""
"Stone is a basic building material and can be dug up by a stone mine. You "
"will also get some raw diamonds from the mine."
msgstr ""
"La pedra és un material bàsic de construcció i pot ser excavada per una mina "
"de pedra. També obtindreu alguns diamants en brut de la mina."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran resource indicator: Stones, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1137 input:1137
#: standard
msgid "There is only a little bit of granite and diamonds here."
msgstr "Aquí només hi ha una mica de granit i diamants."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran resource indicator: Coal, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1148 input:1148
#: standard
msgid "There is a lot of coal here."
msgstr "Aquí hi ha molt carbó."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran resource indicator: Iron, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1159 input:1159
#: standard
msgid "There is a lot of iron ore here."
msgstr "Aquí hi ha molt mineral de ferro."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran resource indicator: Copper-Gold, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1170 input:1170
#: standard
msgid "There is a lot of copper-gold ore here."
msgstr "Aquí hi ha molt mineral de coure-or."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran resource indicator: Stones, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1181 input:1181
#: standard
msgid "There is a lot of granite and diamonds here."
msgstr "Aquí hi ha molt granit i diamants."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Sumatran immovable: Ship Under Construction
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1189 input:1189
#: standard
msgid "A ship is being constructed at this site."
msgstr "En aquest lloc es construeix un vaixell."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Sumatran production site: Headquarters
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1201 input:1201
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"Oh, you brave northern star, you are protecting and watching over all of our "
"buildings. All other stars come and go, but you never leave your place."
msgstr ""
"Oh, valent estrella del nord, estàs protegint i vigilant tots els nostres "
"edificis. Totes les altres estrelles van i vénen, però mai abandones el teu "
"lloc."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Sumatran production site: Headquarters
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1203 input:1203
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid "Part of tribal equinox prayer"
msgstr "Part de l'oració de l'equinocci tribal"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran warehouse: Headquarters
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1205 input:1205
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid "Accommodation for your people. Also stores your wares and tools."
msgstr ""
"Allotjament per a la teva gent. També emmagatzema les teves mercaderies i "
"eines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Sumatran warehouse: Headquarters
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1207 input:1207
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid "The headquarters is your main building."
msgstr "La seu és el vostre edifici principal."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran warehouse: Warehouse
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1214 input:1214
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"Your workers and warriors will find shelter here. Also stores your wares and "
"tools."
msgstr ""
"Els vostres treballadors i guerrers trobaran refugi aquí. També emmagatzema "
"les teves mercaderies i eines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran warehouse: Port
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1221 input:1221
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"Serves as a base for overseas colonization and trade. Also stores your "
"warriors, wares and tools."
msgstr ""
"Serveix com a base per a la colonització i el comerç a l'estranger. També "
"emmagatzema els teus guerrers, mercaderies i eines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran production site: Woodcutter’s House
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1229 input:1229
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"Fells trees in the surrounding area and processes them into logs or tropical "
"wood."
msgstr "Tala arbres dels voltants i els transforma en troncs o fusta tropical."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Sumatran production site: Woodcutter’s House
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1231 input:1231
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"The woodcutter recognizes 3 types of trees. Tropical trees (ironwood, balsa "
"and rubber tree and dipterocarpus), palm trees (5 types of official palms) "
"and all other trees. Trees of the first two groups are cut down only when "
"tropical wood respectively log or palm leaves is needed. If the woodcutter "
"is not able to cut down both tropical and palm trees, the building’s "
"productivity can decrease."
msgstr ""
"El llenyataire reconeix 3 tipus d'arbres. Arbres tropicals (fusta de ferro, "
"balsa i cautxú i dipterocarp), palmeres (5 tipus de palmeres oficials) i la "
"resta d'arbres. Els arbres dels dos primers grups només es tallen quan es "
"necessita fusta tropical, respectivament, troncs o fulles de palmera. Si el "
"llenyataire no és capaç de talar tant palmeres com tropicals, la "
"productivitat de l'edifici pot disminuir."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Sumatran production site: Woodcutter’s House, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1234 input:1234
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"The woodcutter can produce one log between %1$s and %2$s on average, "
"depending on how far he has to walk and how many tree types are available. "
"If there is only one type of trees, if there are two types or tree types, he "
"needs %3$s, %4$s or %5$s on average to cut down one tree respectively."
msgstr ""
"El llenyataire pot produir un tronc entre %1$s i %2$s de mitjana, depenent "
"de la distància que hagi de caminar i de quants tipus d'arbres hi hagi "
"disponibles. Si només hi ha un tipus d'arbres, si hi ha dos tipus o tipus "
"d'arbres, necessita de mitjana %3$s, %4$s o %5$s per talar un arbre "
"respectivament."

