#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Sumatran production site: Palm Planter’s Hut
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1244 input:1244
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"The old legends say that long time ago our tribe lived in a place where only "
"palm trees were growing. Without palm trees we could never call this place "
"our home, they have an irreplaceable place in our culture and economy."
msgstr ""
"Les antigues llegendes diuen que fa molt de temps la nostra tribu vivia en "
"un lloc on només creixien palmeres. Sense palmeres mai podríem anomenar "
"aquest lloc la nostra llar, tenen un lloc insubstituïble en la nostra "
"cultura i economia."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Sumatran production site: Palm Planter’s Hut
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1246 input:1246
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid "Explanation why foresters living in this houses plant palm trees only"
msgstr ""
"Explica per què els forestals que viuen en aquesta casa només planten "
"palmeres"

