#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1248 input:1248
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid "Plants palm trees in the surrounding area."
msgstr "Planta palmeres als voltants."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Sumatran production site: Palm Planter’s Hut
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1250 input:1250
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"You need palm trees for logs, palm wine production and palm leaves, which "
"are collected by leaf gather when a palm tree is cut down."
msgstr ""
"Necessites palmeres per als troncs, la producció de vi de palma i les fulles "
"de palmera, que es recullen per la recollida de fulles quan es tala una "
"palmera."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Sumatran production site: Palm Planter’s Hut, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1253 input:1253
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"The forester plants one palm tree between %1$s and %2$s on average, "
"depending on how far he has to walk."
msgstr ""
"El forestal planta una palmera entre %1$s i %2$s de mitjana, depenent de la "
"distància que hagi de caminar."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran production site: Jungle Preserver’s Hut
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1263 input:1263
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid "Plants tropical trees in the surrounding area."
msgstr "Planta arbres tropicals als voltants."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Sumatran production site: Jungle Preserver’s Hut
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1265 input:1265
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"The tropical trees are source of tropical wood, which is an important "
"building material."
msgstr ""
"Els arbres tropicals són font de fusta tropical, que és un important "
"material de construcció."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Sumatran production site: Jungle Preserver’s Hut, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1268 input:1268
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"The forester plants one tree between %1$s and %2$s on average, depending on "
"how far he has to walk."
msgstr ""
"El forestal planta un arbre entre %1$s i %2$s de mitjana, depenent de la "
"distància que hagi de caminar."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran production site: Stonecutter’s Hut
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1278 input:1278
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid "Cuts raw pieces of stone out of rocks in the vicinity."
msgstr "Talla peces crues de pedra de les roques dels voltants."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Sumatran production site: Stonecutter’s Hut
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1280 input:1280
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid "The stonecutter needs rocks to cut within the work area."
msgstr "El picapedrer necessita pedres per tallar dins de la zona de treball."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Sumatran production site: Stonecutter’s Hut, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1283 input:1283
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"The stonecutter can produce one block of granite between %1$s and %2$s on "
"average, depending on how far he has to walk."
msgstr ""
"El picapedrer pot produir un bloc de granit entre %1$s i %2$s de mitjana, "
"depenent de la distància que hagi de caminar."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran production site: Water Carrier’s Hut
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1293 input:1293
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid "Draws water out of the rivers and lakes."
msgstr "Treu aigua dels rius i llacs."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Sumatran production site: Water Carrier’s Hut
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1295 input:1295
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"Water carriers cannot dig up water from the ground. Roads and trees along "
"the shoreline block drawing water."
msgstr ""
"Els transportistes d'aigua no poden extreure l'aigua del sòl. Els camins i "
"els arbres al llarg de la costa obstrueixen l'aigua."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Sumatran production site: Water Carrier’s Hut, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1298 input:1298
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"The carrier can produce one bucket of water between %1$s and %2$s on "
"average, depending on how far he has to walk."
msgstr ""
"El transportista pot produir una galleda d'aigua entre %1$s i %2$s de "
"mitjana, depenent de la distància que hagi de caminar."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran production site: Leaf Gatherer’s Hut
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1308 input:1308
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"Gathers cassava leaves left by farmers and palm leaves left by woodcutters."
msgstr ""
"Recull fulles de mandioca deixades pels pagesos i fulles de palmera deixades "
"pels llenyataires."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Sumatran production site: Leaf Gatherer’s Hut
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1310 input:1310
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"Both cassava and palm leaves are important wares for your economy and "
"shortages may cause you trouble."
msgstr ""
"Tant la mandioca com les fulles de palmera són productes importants per a la "
"vostra economia i l'escassetat pot causar problemes."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Sumatran production site: Water Carrier’s Hut, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1313 input:1313
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"The leaf gatherer can produce one bundle of leaves between %1$s and %2$s on "
"average, depending on how far she has to walk."
msgstr ""
"El recol·lector de fulles pot produir un paquet de fulles entre %1$s i %2$s "
"de mitjana, depenent de la distància que hagi de caminar."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran production site: Hunter’s Tent
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1323 input:1323
#: standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Hunts animals to produce meat and catches fishes in the waters."
msgstr "Caça animals per produir carn i captura peixos a les aigües."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Sumatran production site: Hunter’s Tent
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1325 input:1325
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"The building has 3 different working areas. Smallest for fishing, larger for "
"hunting and the largest is not used by the worker in this type of building."
msgstr ""
"L'edifici té 3 zones de treball diferents. El més petit per a la pesca, més "
"gran per a la caça i el més gran no és utilitzat pel treballador en aquest "
"tipus d'edifici."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Sumatran production site: Hunter’s Tent, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1328 input:1328
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"If the hunter has both game and fishes in his working area, he needs %1$s to "
"hunt two animals and to catch one fish on average. If there is only one food "
"source available, he needs %2$s to hunt one animal or %3$s to catch one fish "
"on average."
msgstr ""
"Si el caçador té caça i peix a la seva àrea de treball, necessita %1$s per "
"caçar dos animals i capturar un peix de mitjana. Si només hi ha una font "
"d'aliment disponible, necessita %2$s per caçar un animal o %3$s per capturar "
"un peix de mitjana."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran production site: Hunter’s House
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1338 input:1338
#: standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid ""
"Hunts animals to produce meat and catches fishes in the waters. Hunters in "
"this houses can hunt crocodiles for skin and meat too."
msgstr ""
"Caça animals per produir carn i captura peixos a les aigües. Els caçadors "
"d'aquestes cases també poden caçar cocodrils per a la pell i la carn."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Sumatran production site: Hunter’s House
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1340 input:1340
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"The building has 2 different working areas. Smaller for fishing and the "
"larger for hunting."
msgstr ""
"L'edifici té 2 zones de treball diferents. Més petit per a la pesca i més "
"gran per a la caça."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Sumatran production site: Hunter’s House, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1343 input:1343
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"If the hunter has game, crocodiles and fishes in his working area, he needs "
"%1$s to hunt one animal, one crocodile and to catch one fish on average. If "
"there are only two food sources available, he needs %2$s to hunt one animal "
"and one crocodile or %3$s to hunt one animal or crocodile and to catch one "
"fish on average. If there is only one food source available, he needs %4$s "
"to hunt one animal or one crocodile and %5$s to catch one fish on average."
msgstr ""
"Si el caçador té caça, cocodrils i peixos a la seva zona de treball, "
"necessita %1$s per caçar un animal, un cocodril i capturar un peix de "
"mitjana. Si només hi ha dues fonts d'aliment disponibles, necessita %2$s per "
"caçar un animal i un cocodril o %3$s per caçar un animal o cocodril i "
"capturar un peix de mitjana. Si només hi ha una font d'aliment disponible, "
"necessita %4$s per caçar un animal o un cocodril i %5$s per capturar un peix "
"de mitjana."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran production site: Thermal springs, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1354 input:1354
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"Thermal springs make terrain more favorable for tropical and palm trees. "
"This is useful especially while playing wasteland and winter maps. In the "
"first case to transform mountains is very advantageous, in the second case, "
"all types of terrain can be transformed."
msgstr ""
"Les fonts termals fan que el terreny sigui més favorable per a les palmeres "
"tropicals i les palmeres. Això és útil especialment quan es reprodueix a "
"mapes de terres erms i d'hivern. En el primer cas transformar muntanyes és "
"molt avantatjós, en el segon cas es poden transformar tot tipus de terrenys."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran production site: Thermal springs, part 2
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1356 input:1356
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"While playing on White Summer terrains, flowering meadows can be transformed "
"into normal meadows and used for growing palm trees, which are hard to grow "
"on clearings."
msgstr ""
"Mentre es juga en terrenys d'estiu blanc, els prats florits es poden "
"transformar en prats normals i s'utilitzen per fer créixer palmeres, que són "
"difícils de créixer a les clarianes."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Sumatran production site: Thermal springs, the first placeholder is "145 min.", the next three "54"
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1359 input:1359
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"Thermal springs need maintenance. That costs you logs, granite and water."
msgstr ""
"Les fonts termals necessiten manteniment. Això et costa troncs, granit i "
"aigua."

#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1360 input:1360
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"The building needs approximately %1% to improve fertility of every field in "
"its working area. By doing that it will consume approximately %2% logs, %3% "
"buckets of water and %4% blocks of granite."
msgstr ""
"L'edifici necessita aproximadament un 1% per millorar la fertilitat de tots "
"els camps de la seva àrea de treball. En fer-ho, consumirà aproximadament "
"%2% troncs, %3% galledes d'aigua i %4% blocs de granit."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran production site: Scout’s Dwelling
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1367 input:1367
#: standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Explores unknown territory."
msgstr "Explora territoris desconeguts."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran production site: Reed Yard
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1376 input:1376
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid "Produces reed."
msgstr "Produeix canya."

