#: input:1673 input:1682 input:1691 input:1709 standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"If you’re low on warriors to occupy new military sites, use the downward "
"arrow button to decrease the capacity. You can also click on a warrior to "
"send him away."
msgstr ""
"Si teniu pocs guerrers per ocupar nous llocs militars, feu servir el botó de "
"fletxa cap avall per reduir la capacitat. També pots fer clic a un guerrer "
"per enviar-lo."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Sumatran military site: Fortified Tower
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1700 input:1700
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"This building can be built by enhancing a watchtower or big sentry. "
"Enhancement of big sentry costs you one log and one reed more but you save "
"one block of granite instead."
msgstr ""
"Aquest edifici es pot construir millorant una torre de guaita o gran "
"sentinella. La millora d'un gran sentinella us costa un tronc i una canya "
"més, però us estalvieu un bloc de granit."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran production site: Ferry Yard
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1718 input:1718
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid "Builds ferries."
msgstr "Construeix ferris."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Sumatran production site: Ferry Yard, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1723 input:1723
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"The shipwright can produce one ferry between %1$s and %2$s, depending on how "
"far he has to walk."
msgstr ""
"L'armador pot produir un ferri entre %1$s i %2$s, depenent de la distància "
"que hagi de caminar."

