msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"Constructs ships that are used for overseas colonization and for shipping "
"wares between ports."
msgstr ""
"Construeix vaixells que s'utilitzen per a la colonització a l'estranger i "
"per enviar mercaderies entre ports."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Sumatran production site: Shipyard, part 1
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1736 input:1736
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"The shipwright can produce one ship between %1$s and %2$s, depending on how "
"far he has to walk."
msgstr ""
"L'armador pot produir un vaixell entre %1$s i %2$s, depenent de la distància "
"que hagi de caminar."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Sumatran building: Construction Site
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1748 input:1748
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid "‘Don’t swear at the builder who is short of building materials.’"
msgstr "\"No insulteu el constructor que no té materials de construcció\"."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Sumatran building: Construction Site
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1750 input:1750
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid "Proverb widely used for impossible tasks of any kind"
msgstr "Proverbi molt utilitzat per a tasques impossibles de qualsevol tipus"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran building: Construction Site
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1752 input:1752
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid "A new building is being built at this construction site."
msgstr "En aquesta obra s'està construint un nou edifici."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Sumatran building: Dismantle Site
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1759 input:1759
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid "‘New paths will appear when you are willing to tear down the old.’"
msgstr ""
"\"Nous camins apareixeran quan estiguis disposat a enderrocar els vells\"."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Sumatran building: Dismantle Site
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1761 input:1761
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid "Proverb"
msgstr "Proverbi"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Sumatran building: Dismantle Site
#: addons/sumatran_tribe.wad/tribes/sumatran_tribe/units.lua:1763 input:1763
#: standard
msgctxt "sumatran_building"
msgid ""
"A building is being dismantled at this dismantle site, returning some of the "
"resources that were used during this building’s construction to your tribe’s "
"stores."
msgstr ""
"S'està desmantellant un edifici en aquest lloc de desmantellament, retornant "
"alguns dels recursos que es van utilitzar durant la construcció d'aquest "
"edifici a les botigues de la teva tribu."

